I made these for a party the other night but added a few cinnamon sticks, star anise and vanilla beans to the poaching liquid. Served chilled with vanilla ice cream, a sprinkling of carmalized chopped pecans and home made salted caramel sauce. Diners could choose their toppings but the pears on their own were fabulous on their own.

